1️⃣ What is a Modem? Can we connect directly to internet without it?
Modem stands for Modulator Demodulator. It converts digital signals of computer into analog signals and analog into digital signals. It is used to connect computer/network with ISP for internet access. Normally direct internet connection without modem/router possible nahi hota.
 --What is MAC Address? Difference between MAC and IP Address
MAC Address is unique physical address of Network Interface Card (NIC). It is assigned by manufacturer.
Example: 00:1A:2B:3C:4D:5E
Difference:
MAC = Physical address
IP = Logical address
MAC permanent hota hai
IP change ho sakta hai
3️⃣ What is Loopback IP Address? Range
Loopback IP system ko khud test karne ke liye use hota hai.
